00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:55,630
Prime Minister.

291
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:57,100
I did not expect Lord Tian

292
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:58,580
to arrive here in the dead of night.

293
00:13:58,670 --> 00:14:00,120
To what do I owe the honor?

294
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:01,670
Prime Minister.

295
00:14:01,790 --> 00:14:03,960
Are you aware of the recent debates
in the court?

296
00:14:04,350 --> 00:14:05,320
I have been

297
00:14:06,060 --> 00:14:07,510
bedridden.

298
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:08,960
I am not well-versed

299
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:11,360
in matters of the court.

300
00:14:11,470 --> 00:14:13,000
Since His Majesty ascended the throne,

301
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:14,920
he's acted ridiculously

302
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,270
and lived in reckless indulgence.

303
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:17,770
Prime Minister, are you aware of this?

304
00:14:17,810 --> 00:14:20,280
I have heard some whispers.

305
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,480
As the sovereign,

306
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,360
he should be strict with himself.

307
00:14:26,370 --> 00:14:27,960
When the late Emperor passed away,

308
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,200
General Huo

309
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:31,030
supported His Majesty.

310
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:33,720
Since His Majesty
has sunk into indulgence,

311
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:36,600
Lord Huo intends to make amends

312
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:38,820
by choosing another ruler.

313
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,320
Prime Minister,

314
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:45,510
what do you think?

