319
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,600
Then may you rest well

320
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:05,270
and avoid any strain or worry.

321
00:15:05,380 --> 00:15:06,560
It's getting late.

322
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:09,190
I shall take my leave.

323
00:15:10,350 --> 00:15:12,230
Please take care.

324
00:15:25,060 --> 00:15:27,260
This must be handled
with utmost caution.

325
00:15:27,490 --> 00:15:30,150
We'll follow
whatever the Great General decides.

326
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:31,600
Oh, my.

327
00:15:32,410 --> 00:15:35,260
A charge of deceiving the Emperor

328
00:15:35,310 --> 00:15:38,790
