337
00:15:56,390 --> 00:15:57,750
and choose your side early.

338
00:15:57,910 --> 00:15:59,120
If you choose the wrong side,

339
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:01,670
and the Great General succeeds,

340
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:03,690
it will be the day your head falls.

341
00:16:10,520 --> 00:16:11,360
Lord Huo.

342
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,510
I've looked

343
00:16:12,780 --> 00:16:14,120
into Wucheng Village.

344
00:16:14,270 --> 00:16:15,110
Speak.

