350
00:16:23,470 --> 00:16:25,350
De Jiu is closely connected
with these people.

351
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:28,270
Uncle.

352
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:29,460
Much obliged to the heroes.

353
00:16:29,650 --> 00:16:30,840
Our success hinges on this.

354
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,480
More importantly...

355
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,660
