to them, right?

356
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:38,080
Yes.

357
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,320
I fear...

358
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:41,840
We can't allow them to live anymore.

359
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,510
I'm willing to rule the bandits out.

360
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:45,350
Good.

361
00:16:45,670 --> 00:16:46,510
Wait for my command.

